  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Kosodate Quiz My Angel is the first entry in a series of unique quiz simulation games in where players can enjoy assuming the role of a couple of newly parents who must raise their newborn daughter from the age of 0 until the age of 25.\n\nThe Kosodate Quiz series are notable, among other things, for their accessible gameplay mechanics, top-notch presentation and high replay value.",
